             was indicted for <rs id="t17740112-17-off82" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17740112-17-off82" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17740112-17-off82" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing a watch with a silver case, value 40 s. a brass watch key; value 1 d. and nine guineas and 8 s. in money numbered, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17740112-17-victim206" type="victimName">
                           William
                            Foster
                        <interp inst="t17740112-17-victim206" type="surname" value="Foster"></interp>
